Comments:       ----------
                Emulated systems:
                  - Apple II/II+/IIe/Enhanced IIe  - PC Engine/TurboGrafx-16 CD
                  - Atari Lynx                     - SuperGrafx
                  - Neo Geo Pocket (Color)         - PC-FX
                  - WonderSwan                     - Sega Game Gear
                  - GameBoy (Color)                - Sega Genesis/Megadrive
                  - GameBoy Advance                - Sega Master System
                  - Nintendo Entertainment System  - Sega Saturn (64-bit only)
                  - Super Nintendo/Super Famicom   - Sony PlayStation
                  - Virtual Boy
                ----------
                Configuration:
                  - main config file (not required) is ~/.mednafen/mednafen.cfg
                  - example config to start nes emulation in fullscreen:
                      video.fs 1
                      nes.stretch aspect
                  - more configuration options are listed here: 
                https://mednafen.github.io/documentation/#Section_config_files
                ----------
                Quick start guide:
                  - start game: $ mednafen /path/to/rom
                  - toggle fullscreen: Alt+Enter
                  - configure player 1 controls: press Alt+Shift+1 for prompts
                  - configure player 2 controls: press Alt+Shift+2 for prompts
                  - save game state: press number for slot (0-9) then F5
                  - load game state: press number for slot (0-9) then F7
                  - toggle help screen: F1
                  - exit game: Esc or F12
                ----------
                Notes regarding controller configuration:
                  - config settings are written when game exits with Esc or F12
                  - exiting game by closing its window => lost configuration
                  - you should only have to configure controls once per system
                    (i.e., once for nes, once for sega genesis, etc.)
